com.google.template.soy.data.internal

Class DictImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.template.soy.data.SoyAbstractValue
      • com.google.template.soy.data.SoyAbstractMap
        • com.google.template.soy.data.internal.DictImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SoyDict, SoyMap, SoyRecord, SoyValue, SoyValueProvider

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public final class DictImpl
extends SoyAbstractMap
    Internal implementation of SoyDict in terms of a map. Do not use directly; instead, use SoyValueHelper.convert(java.lang.Object).

    Important: Do not use outside of Soy code (treat as superpackage-private).
